      <title>晶体管</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/04/%E6%99%B6%E4%BD%93%E7%AE%A1/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/04/%E6%99%B6%E4%BD%93%E7%AE%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="三级管"><a href="#三级管" class="headerlink" title="三级管"></a>三级管</h1><p>三极管是一个以B(基极)电流Ib 来驱动流过CE 的电流Ic 的器件，工作状态有四个：<strong>放大、截止、饱和、倒置</strong>。<br>&#x2F;&#x2F; 特性：IE &#x3D; IB + IC；IC &#x3D; β * IB；如果 IB &#x3D; 0, 那么 IE &#x3D; IC &#x3D; 0<br>分NPN型和PNP型，此处实例NPN型的，电流从基极和集电极进入，从发射极出，根据基尔霍夫电流定律：<br>当IB&#x3D;0时, IC–&gt;0 ,称为三极管处于<strong>截止</strong>状态，相当于开关断开;<br>当IB&gt;0时, IB轻微的变化,会在IC上以几十甚至百多倍<strong>放大</strong>表现出来;<br>当IB很大时，IC变得很大，不能继续随IB的增大而增大，三极管失去放大功能，表现为开关<strong>导通</strong>。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">              o C: 集电极——————</span><br><span class="line">              |               |</span><br><span class="line">          ——————————          —   +</span><br><span class="line">          |   N    |         ———  —</span><br><span class="line">          ——————————          |</span><br><span class="line">B: 基极o———|   P    | —————————</span><br><span class="line">          ——————————          |</span><br><span class="line">          |   N    |          —   +</span><br><span class="line">          ——————————         ———  —</span><br><span class="line">              |               |</span><br><span class="line">              o E: 发射极———————</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="MOS管"><a href="#MOS管" class="headerlink" title="MOS管"></a>MOS管</h1><p>结构原理：P型半导体衬底，上方扩散两个N型半导体，覆盖SiO2绝缘层，分别腐蚀孔做S源极、G栅极、D漏极；</p><p>特性：一般衬底P和源极S短接一起，加Vds正电压；Vg&#x3D;0时无电流，Vg加超过阈值的正电压时，感应的负电荷把N型区连接起来开始导电；线性区内增大Vg，电阻降低电流增大。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   S       G       D</span><br><span class="line">——————————————————————</span><br><span class="line">|  N  | ooooooo |  N  |</span><br><span class="line">|——————         ——————</span><br><span class="line">|          P          |</span><br><span class="line">|+++++++++++++++++++++|</span><br><span class="line">——————————————————————</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h1><p><a href="https://m.elecfans.com/article/1891386.html">三极管、MOSFET和IGBT的区别-电子发烧友网 (elecfans.com)</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
